{"tid":1382451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈香港人係痴撚線","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:29:24.000Z","uid":253826,"like":1419,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"2abb35748ac1a0de21233254031c1bbcb18417f1","tid":1382451,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，邊撚度<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有一個地方嘅人係咁高質</span></span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n細路，為香港命運出嚟而勇武，用盡家裡一切可用嘅物質：行李箱、煲蓋等等。<br />\n我見到有相有人拎煲蓋當盾時，真係痴撚線！<br />\n點解可以咁嘅look就有勇氣行上前線？<br />\n痴撚線㗎大佬啊！對家用槍用彈㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港，有呢一班細路為我地而戰，絕對係香港人嘅驕傲、光榮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而大人，就做細路嘅強力後盾，無論係替換嘅衣物、回家嘅路、甚至係一餐老麥。<br />\n大人見到細路唔夠錢食飯，即刻上前去資助、支援啊！<br />\n良心老闆仲話要請你地食飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾廿年，未見過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人真係原來可以咁撚團結，咁有人性</span></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">老懷安慰！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請受小弟一拜。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c219f33465445d257e0c61ee894a617d424244c5","tid":1382451,"uid":253826,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"我做咗幾廿年人*"},{"pid":"daa6c273923a3433a43179e30d0a81150158ffc9","tid":1382451,"uid":199727,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"香港人係最高質既！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb73fb6bc75d0f95e75ba9755554c36ed869749","tid":1382451,"uid":249040,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"［飯券義助］推到人道基金、文宣入黎！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c0f7fc82d0073349dd4b91f7b782d2c885959ab","tid":1382451,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"好同意！"},{"pid":"876653b6d925799b6b4d9c42d8b619307ed78207","tid":1382451,"uid":135475,"like":144,"dislike":3,"score":141,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"希望香港成為下一個以色列<br />\n亞洲軍火庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰力第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屠殺大陸新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5423efd293eedf2c51a4f215d551be1440ec6c54","tid":1382451,"uid":37528,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"佢地為我地做咁多，8月5號仲可以返工？"},{"pid":"4be3719fc385ebb24c3727380f3857ef6a1a54ba","tid":1382451,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c316fc401665e546ff225fe447271fcc454649d","tid":1382451,"uid":293677,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"證明香港人同支chi 那na 人唔同Level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca615ebcdee76421ddad0e91569cad3babfadebb","tid":1382451,"uid":299,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"阿媽無咗個蓋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s