aces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24817acd4a57bef3dc10be29f3ee85a6a639659f","tid":1382451,"uid":281528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"5/8大三罷<br />\n多區同時集會"},{"pid":"d4e26199f8f841e5b9a0f46d7b8d7a6f4ede71b1","tid":1382451,"uid":6528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"7fcdf5df45b19f34ee554a994362746d20a01b32","tid":1382451,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"做酒肉朋友基本原則<br />\n<br />\n只談風月 不講正事<br />\n<br />\n提防細作"},{"pid":"4c46e79ca929ab823f595334449bf30748e55973","tid":1382451,"uid":263349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:31:21.000Z","msg":"我屋企有好多木板 單人床 果d木條 唔要 、可以比人 拎返學 整木工 勞作"},{"pid":"360dcf61fa65d9a37df4d6e2ad931be3f33089de","tid":1382451,"uid":165469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"太激動！禁錯負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d714aa5f61fb4fd6656354be30a0a8ad19645e10","tid":1382451,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"要好好愛護佢地！"},{"pid":"4432a823c58529e9defbf77fb6cb8bea62320e33","tid":1382451,"uid":22155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月係我見過香港人咁團結 每次諗到都會眼濕濕"},{"pid":"ea905add2f8c4fd749c0c560e3248029fa41fb11","tid":1382451,"uid":289120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:16:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"240d1ac5e6febac3e2c7b9cd7ff49f8325b05f45","tid":1382451,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e71731cc65625818e77b2891da507bee5206bda0","tid":1382451,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"876653b6d925799b6b4d9c42d8b619307ed78207","tid":1382451,"uid":135475,"like":144,"dislike":3,"score":141,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"希望香港成為下一個以色列<br />\n亞洲軍火庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰力第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屠殺大陸新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"左手支那狗 右手坡豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05428fa60d1aa710b0c2fb883071e6