:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcd27bce6d9aa84f034db58590b726efec02e46f","tid":1382451,"uid":280853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"可惜仲有一班自稱香港土生土長既垃圾，日日係到屌人搞事，見到就嬲。"},{"pid":"aa550c32345c95273920dd406b8fe160f786d1e5","tid":1382451,"uid":65210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2abb35748ac1a0de21233254031c1bbcb18417f1","tid":1382451,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，邊撚度<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有一個地方嘅人係咁高質</span></span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n細路，為香港命運出嚟而勇武，用盡家裡一切可用嘅物質：行李箱、煲蓋等等。<br />\n我見到有相有人拎煲蓋當盾時，真係痴撚線！<br />\n點解可以咁嘅look就有勇氣行上前線？<br />\n痴撚線㗎大佬啊！對家用槍用彈㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港，有呢一班細路為我地而戰，絕對係香港人嘅驕傲、光榮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而大人，就做細路嘅強力後盾，無論係替換嘅衣物、回家嘅路、甚至係一餐老麥。<br />\n大人見到細路唔夠錢食飯，即刻上前去資助、支援啊！<br />\n良心老闆仲話要請你地食飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾廿年，未見過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人真係原來可以咁撚團結，咁有人性</span></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">老懷安慰！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請受小弟一拜。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2772